{"title_page": "Edwin Velasco", "text_new": "{{short description|Colombian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Edwin Velasco\n| image          =\n| image_size     =\n| fullname       = Edwin Alexis Velasco Uzuriaga\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1991|11|5|df=y}}\n| birth_place    = [[Padilla, Cauca|Padilla]], Colombia\n| height         = {{convert|1.78|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}\n| currentclub    = [[Am\u00e9rica de Cali]]\n| clubnumber     = 3\n| position       = [[Defender (association football)|Left back]]\n| youthyears1    = | youthclubs1 = [[Cortulu\u00e1]]\n| years1         = 2011\u20132016\n| clubs1         = [[Cortulu\u00e1]]\n| caps1          = 113\n| goals1         = 0\n| years2         = 2013\n| clubs2         = \u2192 [[Once Caldas]] (loan)\n| caps2          = 2\n| goals2         = 0\n| years3         = 2016\u20132018\n| clubs3         = [[Atl\u00e9tico Nacional]]\n| caps3          = 38\n| goals3         = 1\n| years4         = 2018\u20132019\n| clubs4         = [[Once Caldas]]\n| caps4          = 28\n| goals4         = 2\n| years5         = 2019\u2013\n| clubs5         = [[Am\u00e9rica de Cali]]\n| caps5          = 6\n| goals5         = 1\n| nationalyears1 =\n| nationalteam1  =\n| nationalcaps1  =\n| nationalgoals1 =\n| pcupdate = 00:42, 8 October 2019 (UTC)\n| ntupdate =\n}}\n\n'''Edwin Velasco''' (born 5 November 1991) is a Colombian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|left back]] for [[Am\u00e9rica de Cali]].\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Soccerway|edwin-alexis-velasco-uzuriaga/216618}}\n\n{{Am\u00e9rica de Cali squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Velasco, Edwin}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Colombian footballers]]\n[[Category:Atl\u00e9tico Nacional footballers]]\n[[Category:Once Caldas footballers]]\n[[Category:Cortulu\u00e1 footballers]]\n[[Category:Am\u00e9rica de Cali footballers]]\n[[Category:Categor\u00eda Primera A players]]\n[[