a A players]]\n[[Category:Categor\u00eda Primera B players]]\n[[Category:Association football fullbacks]]\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Colombian footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"association football player\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edwin_Velasco"}
