ation football forwards]]\n\n{{colombia-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Orphan|date=February 2013}}\n\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Elvis Rivas\n| image = \n| fullname = Elvis Antonio Rivas Palacios\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1987|2|19}}\n| birth_place = [[Quibd\u00f3]], [[Colombia]]\n| height = 5 ft 7 in\n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]], [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub =\n| clubnumber =\n| youthyears1 = \u20132005\n| youthclubs1 = [[C\u00facuta Deportivo]]\n| years1 = 2006\u20132008\n| clubs1 = [[C\u00facuta Deportivo]]\n| caps1 = \n| goals1 = 1\n| years2 = 2009\n| clubs2 = [[Atl\u00e9tico Bucaramanga]]\n| caps2 = \n| goals2 =\n| years3 = 2010\n| clubs3 = [[Deportivo Pasto]]\n| caps3 =\n| goals3 =1\n| years4 = 2011\n| clubs4 = [[Sucre FC|Pac\u00edfico FC]]\n| caps4 = 11\n| goals4 = 0\n| years5 = 2012\n| clubs5 = [[Atl\u00e9tico Bucaramanga]]\n| caps5 = 6\n| goals5 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 = \n| nationalcaps1 = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| pcupdate = December 2, 2012\n}}\n\n'''Elvis Antonio Rivas Palacios''' (born February 19, 1987) is a Colombian football defender.<ref>[http://www.bdfa.com.ar/jugadores-ELVIS-ANTONIO-RIVAS-43956.html Profile at BDFA]</ref>\n\nHe was part of Cucuta 2006 Colombian 1st division Championship and helped Cucuta get to the semi finals of the [[Copa Libertadores 2007]]\n\n==Honors==\n* Champions Colombian Primera A, 2006 Deportivo Cucuta\n* Semi Finalist of Copa Libertories with Cucuta in 2007\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rivas, Elvis}}\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Colombian footballers]]\n[[Category:C\u00facuta Deportivo footballers]]\n[[Category:Atl\u00e9tico Bucaramanga footballers]]\n[[Category:Deportivo Pasto footballers]]\n[[Category:Colombian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Bolivia]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]] \n[[Category:Association footbal